metadata.name: G0D'S - EYE
metadata.description:
This 1/1 Art piece was created with Neural Network Machine Learning Technology generating an input I chose titled "God's eye"
This was then generated around a 3D render I created depicting an eyeball.

Software used - Cinema4D / VQGAN+CLIP / Soundly / Adobe After Effects

Artwork and Sound design by NVNEIK
